<i>THIS IS THE DIMENSION
OF IMAGINATION</i>

00:32.491 --> 00:35.984
<i>IT IS AN AREA WHICH WE
CALL THE TWILIGHT ZONE.</i>

00:36.078 --> 00:38.319
<i>[music intensifies
dramatically]</i>

00:42.584 --> 00:44.996
<i>[cheerful music]</i>

00:56.014 --> 00:57.846
