01:09.194 --> 01:11.856
<i>(male presenter, off)
STREET SCENE</i>

01:11.947 --> 01:13.733
<i>SUMMER, THE PRESENT.</i>

01:13.824 --> 01:17.192
<i>MAN ON THE SIDEWALK
NAMED LOU BOOKMAN.</i>

01:17.244 --> 01:20.362
<i>AGE, SIXTYISH.
