01:20.414 --> 01:24.078
<i>LOU BOOKMAN,
A FIXTURE OF THE SUMMER.</i>

01:24.167 --> 01:27.080
<i>A RATHER MINOR COMPONENT
TO A HOT JULY.</i>

01:27.170 --> 01:29.878
<i>A NONDESCRIPT
COMMONPLACE LITTLE MAN,</i>

01:29.965 --> 01:31.672
<i>WHOSE LIFE IS A TREADMILL</i>

01:31.758 --> 01:35.126
<i>BUILT OUT OF SIDEWALKS.</i>

01:35.220 --> 01:37.006
<i>IN JUST A MOMENT,
LOU BOOKMAN</i>

01:37.097 --> 01:39.680
<i>WILL HAVE TO CONCERN
HIMSELF WITH SURVIVAL.</i>

01:39.766 --> 01:42.474
<i>BECAUSE AS OF 3 O'CLOCK
THIS HOT JUL YAFTERNOON</i>

01:42.561 --> 01:46.304
<i>HE'LL BE STALKED
