A CENSUS TAKER?

03:47.728 --> 03:51.016
BORN IN NEW YORK
CITY IN 1890.

03:51.106 --> 03:53.848
THAT'S RIGHT, 1890.

03:53.900 --> 03:57.063
FATHER JACOB BOOKMAN,
MOTHER FLORA BOOKMAN.

03:57.154 --> 03:59.441
FATHER'S PLACE OF BIRTH,
DETROIT, MICHIGAN,

03:59.531 --> 04:02.114
MOTHER'S PLACE OF BIRTH
SYRACUSE, NEW YORK, RIGHT?

04:02.200 --> 04:04.532
