IN THAT BOOK THERE.

04:06.621 --> 04:09.204
YES, WE HAVE TO KEEP
THESE THINGS EFFICIENT.

04:09.249 --> 04:12.537
NOW TODAY
IS THE 19TH OF JULY.

04:12.627 --> 04:15.005
