ASK ME A LOT OF QUESTIONS.

04:55.837 --> 04:57.453
WHAT GENTLEMAN?

04:57.547 --> 04:59.003
<i>[ominous music]</i>

04:59.090 --> 05:00.376
THAT GENTLEMAN!

05:02.511 --> 05:04.673
WHAT GENTLEMAN?

