05:09.935 --> 05:11.642
WHY NOT WHAT, LOU?

05:11.728 --> 05:13.514
WHY CAN'T YOU
SEE HIM OR HEAR HIM?

05:13.605 --> 05:16.518
SEE WHO, LOU?

05:16.608 --> 05:18.770
IT WORKS GREAT NOW, LOU.

