05:25.867 --> 05:27.949
OH, YEAH. GOOD BYE, LOU.
THANKS A LOT!

05:28.036 --> 05:30.368
NO, NO, I MEAN
TO THE GENTLEMAN THERE.

05:30.455 --> 05:32.446
OH, IT'S A GAME.

05:32.541 --> 05:35.454
THE INVISIBLE MAN.
GOODBYE, INVISIBLE MAN.

05:35.544 --> 05:36.875
SEE YOU
AFTER SUPPER, LOU.

05:42.968 --> 05:44.959
<i>[suspense music]</i>

05:45.053 --> 05:49.547
I CAN SEE YOU,
YET SHE CAN'T.

05:49.641 --> 05:52.975
<i>(Mr. Death) ONLY THOSE WHO ARE
TO ACCOMPANY ME CAN SEE ME.</i>

05:53.019 --> 05:55.226
<i>UNDERSTAND, MR. BOOKMAN?</i>

05:55.313 --> 05:57.600
<i>UH, MR. BOOK MA N,</i>

06:00.777 --> 06:03.690
ONLY THOSE THAT ARE
TO ACCOMPANY ME CAN SEE ME.

06:03.780 --> 06:07.068
NOVV DON'T YOU THINK YOU OUGHT TO
START MAKING YOUR ARRANGEMENTS?

06:07.158 --> 06:08.740
