UNDERSTAND YOU PEOPLE.

06:17.419 --> 06:20.081
YOU GET THE IDIOTIC NOTION
THAT LIFE GOES ON FOREVER.

06:20.171 --> 06:21.457
OF COURSE, IT DOESN'T.

06:21.548 --> 06:23.038
EVERYONE HAS
TO GO SOMETIME.

06:23.133 --> 06:24.999
GO? YOU MEAN--

06:25.093 --> 06:27.755
THAT'S RIGHT. AND VVHAT I
FURTHER DON'T UNDERSTAND

06:27.846 --> 06:30.679
