06:35.312 --> 06:37.269
WE'RE NOT PERMITTED
TO FOREWARN THEM.

06:37.355 --> 06:40.723
YOU, MR. BOOKMAN,
FALL INTO THE CATEGORY

06:40.817 --> 06:42.353
OF "NATURAL CAUSES."

06:42.444 --> 06:44.060
"NATURAL CAUSES?"

06:44.154 --> 06:46.862
NUMBER ONE, I FIND YOU
A VERY DEVIOUS SORT,

06:46.948 --> 06:48.450
