DO YOU WANT IT?

06:59.628 --> 07:01.335
IF YOU STILL
DON'T KNOW WHO I AM

07:01.421 --> 07:03.913
THEN YOU'RE THE DUMBEST
MAN I'VE COME UP AGAINST.

07:08.094 --> 07:09.676
<i>[intense ominous music]</i>

07:17.562 --> 07:19.724
YOU ARE--
YOU'RE DEATH?

07:19.814 --> 07:22.101
EXACTLY, MR. BOOKMAN.

07:22.192 --> 07:25.981
<i>NOW, SHALL WE GET
DOWN TO BUSINESS?</i>

07:26.071 --> 07:28.904
TIME OF DEPARTURE
IS MIDNIGHT TONIGHT.

07:28.990 --> 07:30.822
I TRUST THAT
WILL SUIT YOU.

07:30.909 --> 07:33.571
PREORDINATION IS
FOR DEATH DURING SLEEP.

07:33.662 --> 07:36.575
I ASSUME THIS TOO VVILL
MEET VVITH YOUR APPROVAL.

07:36.665 --> 07:39.783
YOU'LL FIND THIS A RELATIVELY
SIMPLE AND PAINLESS-

07:39.876 --> 07:41.787
NO, JUST A MINUTE.
I DON'T WANNA GO!

07:41.878 --> 07:43.835
NO, THEY NEVER DO.

07:43.922 --> 07:46.835
BUT THERE'S NO REASON TO GO.
I'M A VERY HEALTHY MAN!

07:46.925 --> 07:50.259
OUTSIDE OF A SLIGHT COLD
I HAD LAST WINTER,

07:50.303 --> 07:53.466
AND A SLIVER THAT FESTERED
IN THAT FINGER THERE,

07:53.556 --> 07:56.048
I DON'T THINK I'VE HAD
A SICK DAY IN 2O YEARS!

07:56.142 --> 07:57.678
THAT MAY BE,

07:57.769 --> 07:59.931
BUT DEPARTURE TIME
IS SET FOR MIDNIGHT.

07:59.980 --> 08:02.221
AND DEPARTURE
WILL BE MIDNIGHT.

08:02.315 --> 08:04.522
DON'T I HAVE ANYTHING
TO SAY ABOUT THAT?

08:04.609 --> 08:06.691
WE DO LISTEN TO APPEALS

08:06.778 --> 08:09.440
BUT FRANKLY, MR. BOOKMAN,
THERE'S VERY LITTLE HERE

08:09.531 --> 08:11.693
