EXTENUATING CIRCUMSTANCE.

08:11.783 --> 08:14.115
THERE ARE THREE MAJOR
CATEGORIES OF APPEALS.

08:14.202 --> 08:15.613
ONE, IS HARDSHIP CASES.

08:15.704 --> 08:17.615
NOW DO YOU
HAVE A WIFE OR FAMILY

08:17.706 --> 08:20.949
VVHO MIGHT SUFFER BEYOND A
REASONABLE POINT YOUR DEMISE?

08:21.001 --> 08:24.915
[softly]
NO, NO FAMILY. NO.

08:25.005 --> 08:28.373
THE SECOND CATEGORY
IS PRIORITY CASES

08:28.466 --> 08:31.549
STATESMEN, SCIENTISTS, MEN
ON THE VERGE OF DISCOVERIES.

08:31.636 --> 08:37.881
I TAKE IT YOU'RE NOT VVORKING ON ANY
MAJOR SCIENTIFIC PURSUIT AT THE MOMENT.

08:37.976 --> 08:40.138
[softly]
NO [chuckles] NO.

08:40.186 --> 08:42.644
[firmly]
WHAT'S THE THIRD CATEGORY?

08:42.731 --> 08:45.974
I DON'T THINK YOU'RE
QUALIFIED HERE EITHER.

08:46.067 --> 08:49.401
UNFINISHED BUSINESS
OF A MAJOR NATURE.

08:49.487 --> 08:52.900
YOU DON'T HAVE ANY
UNFINISHED BUSINESS, DO YOU?

08:52.991 --> 08:54.026
AH, BUT I DO!

08:54.117 --> 08:55.482
INDEED I DO!

08:55.535 --> 08:58.152
THAT'S IT,
YOU SEE. I-- YEAH.

08:58.246 --> 09:00.408
I HAVE SOME
UNFINISHED BUSINESS.

09:00.498 --> 09:03.206
UNFINISHED BUSINESS, YES.

09:06.004 --> 09:09.588
I'VE NEVER FLOWN
IN A HELICOPTER. THAT'S IT.

09:09.674 --> 09:11.256
I'VE NEVER FLOWN--

09:11.342 --> 09:13.754
<i>(Death)
INSUFFICIENT, MR. BOOKMAN.</i>

09:16.347 --> 09:18.338
<i>ANYTHING ELSE?</i>

09:18.391 --> 09:22.100
NOVV YOU LOOK HERE. I'VE LIVED
IN THIS ROOM FOR 21 YEARS.

09:22.187 --> 09:25.896
