09:25.982 --> 09:27.723
WILL YOU PLEASE
STAY IN ONE PLACE?

09:27.817 --> 09:30.525
IS THERE ANYTHING
ELSE, MR. BOOKMAN?

09:30.570 --> 09:32.072
YES, YES.

09:32.155 --> 09:34.943
I HAVE NEVER SEEN
A ZULU WAR DANCE.

09:35.033 --> 09:37.400
NOW THAT'S
THE ANSWER RIGHT THERE.

09:37.494 --> 09:41.078
SO YOU'LL HAVE TO GIVE ME A COUPLE OF
MONTHS TO GO OVER TO THAT ZULU COUNTRY

09:41.164 --> 09:43.371
NO?

09:43.458 --> 09:45.916
NO. UNFINISHED BUSINESS
OF A MAJOR NATURE

09:46.002 --> 09:48.118
<i>IS SOMETHING A MAN
HAD YEARNED FOR</i>

09:48.213 --> 09:50.955
<i>AND SOMETHING HE MIGHT
ACCOMPLISH GIVEN AN EXTENSION.</i>

09:51.049 --> 09:53.837
WELL, THERE IS ONE THING.

09:53.927 --> 09:56.214
WHAT IS IT, MR. BOOKMAN?

09:56.262 --> 09:59.050
WELL, BETWEEN YOU AND ME,

09:59.099 --> 10:01.761
