A TRULY BIG PITCH.

10:01.851 --> 10:04.639
I MEAN, I MEAN
A BIG PITCH.

10:04.729 --> 10:08.893
A PITCH BIG ENOUGH
FOR THE SKIES TO OPEN UP.

10:08.983 --> 10:12.396
<i>YOU KNOW,
A PITCH FOR THE ANGELS.</i>

10:12.445 --> 10:15.062
OF COURSE, IT WOULDN'T
MEAN VERY MUCH TO YOU,

10:15.115 --> 10:16.901
BUT IT WOULD MEAN
A GREAT DEAL TO ME.

10:16.991 --> 10:19.244
<i>IT WOULD MEAN
THAT FOR ONE MOMENT</i>

10:19.285 --> 10:23.153
<i>IN MY WHOLE LIFE I WOULD HAVE
DONE SOMETHING SUCCESSFUL.</i>

10:23.248 --> 10:28.288
