10:41.057 --> 10:42.923
UNTIL I MAKE A PITCH!

10:43.017 --> 10:45.509
THE KIND OF PITCH
I WAS TALKING TO YOU ABOUT.

10:45.603 --> 10:46.980
THE ONE FOR THE ANGELS?

10:47.063 --> 10:49.555
THAT'S RIGHT.
ONE FOR THE ANGELS.

10:51.943 --> 10:54.355
I'M TERRIBLY SORRY,
MR. BOOKMAN,

10:54.445 --> 10:56.186
BUT, NO.

10:58.324 --> 11:00.986
<i>YOU SEE, THESE CATEGORIES
ARE VERY SPECIFIC</i>

11:01.077 --> 11:04.490
AND VVHEN REFERENCE IS MADE TO
UNFINISHED BUSINESS OF A MAJOR NATURE,

11:04.581 --> 11:06.572
