TO BE MADE HERE

11:06.666 --> 11:08.168
IS SIMPLY THAT--

11:10.461 --> 11:12.543
WHAT-- WHAT I MEAN
IS THAT, UH,

11:12.630 --> 11:14.621
UNFORTUNATELY, MR. BOOKMAN,

11:14.674 --> 11:17.507
AN ABILITY TO, TO SUCCEED

11:17.594 --> 11:19.380
